1: The Lord rules. He is dressed with great power. The Lord has dressed Himself with strength. For sure, the world is built to last. It will not be moved.
2: Your throne is set up from long ago. You have always been.
3: The floods have lifted up, O Lord. The floods have lifted up their voice. The floods lift up their beating waves.
4: The Lord on high is more powerful than the sound of many waters and the strong waves of the sea.
5: Your Word is very sure. O Lord, Your house is holy forever.
